      Product description

      This beautiful ball gown has a overlay and ruching at the side seam from ADIVA. This dress will look great with our bridesmaids ball gown styles. It is sleeveless Gown, has v-neck with flower and gota work. This style features an adjustable fit for added flexibility and comfort with fewer alterations. Made from net, very light in weight and self design pattern. This product is available in defferet color black, blue, pink, peach, navy blue, red, white, yellow, and coral. Adiva launches latest in trend collection of dresses. Adiva is a leading brand in kids wear for girls with wide range of kids clothing which includes dresses, lehenga choli, churidar suits, gowns, frocks and a lot more.

      How are ratings calculated?
      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
